Question will be suspended the day before the date of interest and resolved when the data is released, usually on Monday of the following week. Confused? Check our FAQ or ask us for help.

column6: It looks like they are really narrowing the bins compared to previous questions. I'm going to start changing things up for these economic indicator forecasts by using a mixed methods approach in R (https://robjhyndman.com/hyndsight/forecast-combinations/). To assign the probabilities to each bin I am hazardously overstating my confidence by using the standard deviation calculated in the automatic ARIMA model fitting function (this isn't really valid and I might as well be picking a std dev out of a hat, but hey, this is a land of experimentation).
